---
title: Hearty Turkey Stew with Herby Croutons
description: This heart-warming bowl of turkey stew is jam-packed with wholesome goodness! While you cook, you'll be tempted to snack on those crunchy croutons (trust us). We say go for it, just make sure some of them make it onto the stew!

